⸻

6) If GNU Radio does not have “Interleaved Short To Complex”

Use this chain instead:

TCP Source (byte) -> Stream to Vector (len=2) -> Char/Short conversion path

But most standard installs have Interleaved Short To Complex, and that is the easiest path.

⸻

7) Important note on performance

Start at:

* 250e3 or 500e3

Do not start at multi-megasample rates yet. Once you confirm the host spectrograph works, you can step up.

